 # 24 反转链表

### 题目

定义一个函数，输入一个链表的头节点，反转该链表并输出反转后链表的头节点


### 解答


##### 1. 快慢双指针
```
/JAVA/
class Solution {
    public ListNode reverseList(ListNode head) {
        if (head == null) {
            return null;
        }
        ListNode fast = head.next;
        ListNode slow = head;
        while (fast != null) {
            ListNode node = fast.next;
            fast.next = slow;
            slow = fast;
            fast = node;
        }
        head.next = null;
        return slow;
    }
}
```
##### 2. 递归
```
/js/
var reverseList = function(head) {
    if (head == null) return null;
    var callbackReverseList = function(head) {
        if (head.next == null) {
            return head;
        }
        let node = callbackReverseList(head.next);
        head.next.next = head;
        return node;
    }
    var res = callbackReverseList(head);
    head.next = null;
    return res;
};
```
